    "description": "<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/848700d768fe6d866d41bab59e6c377d.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/848700d768fe6d866d41bab59e6c377d.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/848700d768fe6d866d41bab59e6c377d.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是时候集结您的亡灵部队了，殿下！</h2>欢迎来到NecroCity，它结合了城市建造、战略和塔防。保卫你的不死前哨免受所谓的“善良”顽强力量的侵袭！召集你的骷髅大军，向活着的人们展示你们骨头里嘎嘎作响的力量！告诉亡灵世界你不再是孩子了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/4e1f0e5b831254d6a6204497ea259af3.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/4e1f0e5b831254d6a6204497ea259af3.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/4e1f0e5b831254d6a6204497ea259af3.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >等等，什么？</h2>没错，你的角色是一名年轻的亡灵王子，并努力证明自己的价值。建造新的前哨基地，在大地上广播亡灵王国的荣耀。召唤工人，挖掘骨头，捕捉灵魂，并不惜一切代价保护你的通灵塔。安置陷阱，招募幽灵和骷髅，使用魔法，添加模组来为你的游戏增加趣味，或者向你的食尸鬼朋友们寻求帮助。选择最佳的策略，这一切都取决于你！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/5d9083072ab7144f49c3dbae451ec542.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/5d9083072ab7144f49c3dbae451ec542.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/5d9083072ab7144f49c3dbae451ec542.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是时候证明自己了！</h2>在官僚巫妖王的统治下，亡灵王国一片秩序井然。直到他的弟弟开始证明自己的能力，并意外地得到了他所应得的。帮助年轻王子在繁碌的世界中建造新的前哨站，并保护它们免受顽固英雄和其他善良力量的侵袭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/a607de9288bd7da00f931e59fb621ad6.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/a607de9288bd7da00f931e59fb621ad6.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/a607de9288bd7da00f931e59fb621ad6.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造和保卫你的前哨</h2>在各种基于网格的地图上建造你的前哨站。召唤可爱的骷髅工人来收集和生产资源，并使用(Necro)Energy™为你的建筑供电。<br><br>探索地形，适应周围环境，并准备好面对一波又一波的敌人攻击。在游戏中，使用主动暂停来制定你的策略。建造强大的防御工事，使用墙来阻挡你的敌人，并战略性地安置陷阱。建造营房和塔楼将你的工人变成致命的士兵。并采用一系列被动式建筑和模组，进一步地加强你的防御。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/687543563b63f6a5224dfbcf07edcb99.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/687543563b63f6a5224dfbcf07edcb99.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/687543563b63f6a5224dfbcf07edcb99.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >编辑你自己！ 编辑你的朋友！</h2>使用独特的模组系统，你可以改变防御的工作方式。为你的火球添加连锁闪电，或使用你敌人的生命力来治疗你的士兵！或者两者兼而有之？混合搭配不同的模组，可以更好地匹配你所处的情况。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/a7a57f88739e94e48ff166f05637bd96.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/a7a57f88739e94e48ff166f05637bd96.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/a7a57f88739e94e48ff166f05637bd96.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >结交难得的盟友！</h2>结识一群有趣的人士，并成为他们的朋友。然后派他们去战场上为你战斗！发现新的盟友，倾听他们的讨论，学习他们的技能并升级它们，使其变得更强大。选择何时部署和使用他们的技能，因为好的时机可以扭转战局。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/96ee3f5e97d43d21db4ac32d898a692e.poster.avif?t=1717747604\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/96ee3f5e97d43d21db4ac32d898a692e.webm?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489310/extras/96ee3f5e97d43d21db4ac32d898a692e.mp4?t=1717747604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
